# <type>: <short summary>
#
# <detailed explanation of what changed and why>
#
# <technical details, root cause analysis, or context>
#
# <any relevant metrics, performance data, or examples>
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Type Prefixes:
#   feat:     New feature
#   fix:      Bug fix
#   perf:     Performance improvement
#   refactor: Code refactoring
#   docs:     Documentation changes
#   test:     Test additions or modifications
#   chore:    Build, tooling, or maintenance tasks
#
# Guidelines:
#   - Short summary: imperative mood, lowercase, no period
#   - Explain WHAT and WHY, not just HOW
#   - Include metrics for performance changes
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
